and honestly, it’s so incredible how much they’ve changed over the years.

Before, even during TATINOF, when they posted videos it felt like they both, especially Dan, were putting on a character and basically acting the entire time and these days their videos are so much more,,, genuine??

Like??

They’re so much more open with their personalities and all and it’s so sweet??
